<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-fra-mandats-de-paiement.md" sourcestartlinenumber="65"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-fra-mandats-de-paiement.md" sourcestartlinenumber="65">Invoice lines that have not been reviewed by the director.</p>
